Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:01.44,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:04.44,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,take my hand in marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:08.24,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:11.48,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist, I'll marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:20.75,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuu-chan, look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:24.58,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga-chan gave birth to so many puppies!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.95,0:00:29.24,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,They're your kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:35.92,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,A dream, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:40.09,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's finally summer break...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:43.43,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having these dreams because of the stupid DVDs we rented.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.11,0:00:49.25,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Even for a dream, that's one awful future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.45,0:00:51.57,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:53.71,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I had a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.50,0:00:57.74,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You were a dog, and my husband was the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:00:58.82,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:01.00,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,it was a horrible dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:33.81,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,A premonition?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:34.46,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:40.93,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It was a warning, telling me that if I don't work out a counter-plan, {\i1}that{\i0} future awaits me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:42.14,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That dream was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:44.96,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,So, in order to change the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:50.13,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,one side should fully support the other starting with the trip tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.55,0:02:52.18,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:54.15,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why badminton?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.15,0:02:55.36,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:56.97,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,we're going to decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.49,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Decide who's doing what!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:04.00,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, be careful when using the stove.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:06.50,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Stir the rice bran once a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:08.98,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure to change Inko-chan's water in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:10.57,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Read the rest in the note I left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:13.38,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:17.42,Default,Yasuko,0000,0000,0000,,Going? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:20.17,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I? On a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:22.15,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Yacchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:28.96,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the weather's going to be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:32.47,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm counting on you... for {\i1}that{\i0} plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:38.23,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you sure it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:41.23,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's your win, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:43.03,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Get this thing off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:48.82,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for that dumb dog getting involved, I would have won!{trespassing didnt fit here :\}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:53.76,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It was punishment for setting up a match in something you're good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:56.60,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. Nothing good ever comes out of anything involving dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:00.71,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Still... will it really go smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:02.05,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:06.30,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,When this trip is over, your relationship with Minorin will be—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:07.50,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:08.97,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.82,0:04:11.26,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:13.03,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,You're right on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.61,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Fabulous! Simply fabulous!{this stays or RAGE}{furthermore... ts it to the colors of the rainbow ("fabulous")}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:20.28,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?! Where's the energy?! Make some noise! {Missing line after this where Ryuuji says "Y-Yeah..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:21.98,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:21.29,Default-alt,Random,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:22.00,Default-alt,Random,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{uwaaa}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:25.03,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,My, the weather has become perfect for an outing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.04,Default-alt,Random,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{micha ikemasen}Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:26.41,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.71,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, A-min's not here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.71,0:04:30.87,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,There's still some time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.57,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I've got an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:33.33,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:33.33,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:34.93,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:39.56,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Where are those guys? There's nobody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:41.21,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.50,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,You're two minutes late, Ami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:45.55,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, A-min!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:47.77,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, stupid chihuahua.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:53.10,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:55.01,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't run away, stupid chihuahua!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:56.73,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Ami, we're right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:06.69,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.69,0:05:09.25,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,There's a plum in this that makes it super plum!{yes she's doing a horrible pun here - kaze approves yet kinda wants to reword it}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:09.94,Default-alt,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:11.27,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Want to marry into my family?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:11.95,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:14.59,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, you're mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:15.69,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:17.10,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:20.03,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,it seems Aisaka-san didn't come. Is she late?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:21.42,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, go get in touch with—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:25.74,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.74,0:05:28.50,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? The stupid chi' is awake?{starting this episode, Taiga is shortening down stupid chihuahua to stupid 'hua -> bakachiwawa = bakachi}{so it should be "stupid chi'" to match accordingly which is pronounced the same for the dog name anyway}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.81,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were sleeping with your eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:31.45,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:33.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight when we're on a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:37.48,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That aside, what have you been doing during summer break so far, Kawashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.77,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.80,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I've been working the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:42.40,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you started working again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.89,0:05:43.95,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What about Minorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:48.61,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Club activities, work, club activities, work, club activities, club activities, work,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.99,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,club activities, work, club activities, work, club...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:50.99,Default-alt,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What about you, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:52.54,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.40,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:56.91,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I was making this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:06.25,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just now, I heard "senpai" in a strange voice! Is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:07.03,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:10.51,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Sampled from CD's with more to them than just what they advertised — a collection of spirit voices.{いわくつきのCDから集めた心霊音声集}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:11.92,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:15.24,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,No~! I've been called out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:17.93,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka likes those kinds of horror things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.93,0:06:20.90,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I might like them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:22.34,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:25.46,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's also rather surprising that Kushieda's scared of eerie things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:26.67,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared of it, I'm scared of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:28.20,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm super scared of it, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:30.03,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than super scared, you could say I'm incredibly scared—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:35.54,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, you see, is {\i1}really{\i0} scared of horror movies, spirits, and occult things in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:36.58,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:41.10,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're going to scare Minorin to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:46.00,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Then you're going to save her when she's at the peak of her fear.{I'm not sure how you say when someone's at the very height of being frightened in english, so I tried.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:48.34,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,With a, "I will protect Kushieda!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:52.55,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,This is called the "Scare Minorin, Enter the White Knight!" plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:53.89,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Either way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:56.49,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Scary things are absolutely forbidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.87,0:07:02.27,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:23.21,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... how far do we have to walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:24.99,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You can see it already, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:25.50,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.92,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go around the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:29.69,Default,AMi,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going that way and I think we'll be on the balcony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:33.99,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,This is A-min's vacation home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:35.42,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be staying here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:36.91,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Minori-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:38.89,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! I'm so moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:42.48,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,But... we've got to clean the place up first...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.34,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's been here since last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:45.82,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,S-Since last year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:46.77,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:50.78,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,This looks like it'll be one hell of a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:54.23,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,What?! We've got this pretty sea right in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:56.22,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{souji nanka}Let's leave cleaning up for last!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:57.45,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.22,0:07:58.38,Default-alt,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We can clean later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:08:00.09,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:03.22,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going too... What about you, Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:20.85,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I cleaning all by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:25.98,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:26.65,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:29.21,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.07,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:32.03,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,kinda looks like someone's head, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:35.04,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, it's a floating corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:39.24,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?! I've been soaked in corpse water!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.26,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:42.16,Default-alt,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sorry, Minorin! That might be seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.54,Default-alt,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wah, then it's a seaweed corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:49.19,Default-alt,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What should I do?! I've been soaked in seaweed corpse water!{I can't make out any more of these lines.... maybe omit them?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:45.54,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You really came, Yuusaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.35,0:08:47.42,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:52.02,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have Takasu come without his good friend coming along as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:54.67,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You sure about this? What about the student council?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:57.87,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:00.39,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:02.96,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.04,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Ami said to go out shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:07.23,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently there's a bike in the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:07.81,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:11.30,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, take Taiga with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:12.96,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Take Aisaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:16.42,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:18.07,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared of bikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:18.66,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.35,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:23.75,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.12,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:31.25,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You finally had a chance to be alone together. {re-time to after the sigh}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:33.85,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I had an idea, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:39.64,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Before they come back, we've got to find somewhere suitable to play out {\i1}that{\i0} plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You're just embarrassed, just admi—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:44.31,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,There was a mosquito there, a mosquito!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:46.81,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:49.42,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say "somewhere suitable"...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.84,0:09:53.08,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:54.03,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,a bathroom, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:55.83,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta clean here too—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:56.61,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:57.76,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:59.49,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I didn't notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:00.44,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:02.15,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll get out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:03.36,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.54,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You're really bold, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.81,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Coming in while a girl's showering...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:10.74,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like I did it on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.93,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. We can keep it a secret from everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.93,0:10:15.73,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What are you say—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:17.57,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:19.26,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:21.05,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Clean the bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:25.20,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh! What were you expecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:28.48,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that face?! It's a masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.90,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga~!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:34.94,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Stupid chi' did?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:37.54,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Making it sound like she was taking a shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:40.17,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Playing with a man's pure heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:43.66,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And? Did you finish investigating the second floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:45.48,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:48.78,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you got tricked by the likes of the stupid chi'!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:51.19,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I'll go check!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:53.71,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And while I'm at it, I'm going to tell her off as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:57.58,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stupid chi'!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:09.51,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,The stupid chi' was actually in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.11,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,The stupid chi' was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:13.33,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,BOOM!{right breast}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:14.57,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And BOOM!{left breast}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:16.78,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,And here, it was EXPLODING!{ami doesn't shave downstairs.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:18.82,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say unnecessary things!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.35,0:11:22.63,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:25.08,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You sure bought a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.08,0:11:25.75,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kitamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.06,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,He's putting the bike away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:28.45,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.95,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I'll carry them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:30.91,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.36,0:11:33.62,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda did the shopping, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:34.42,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.91,0:11:38.25,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:42.11,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right now, something... on my — on my neck... {re-time to "ima"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:43.49,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:45.64,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{sou da yo ne...}Y-You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.01,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{sou da yo ne!}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.76,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{ima tashika ni}Something definitely touched me just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:52.52,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{nuru tte iuka}Something slippery... like seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:55.73,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{y-yappari}I-It really does smell like seaweed! It's seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.52,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{wakame ni maki-}Like an animal spirit entwined in seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.82,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{rakko? wakame-}A sea otter? When it comes to being entwined in seaweed, it has to be the corpse of a sea otter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:01.93,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{kawa no poketto}A sea otter with its stomach pocket filled with scallops?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.61,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{rakko to wakame no noroi da!}It's the curse of the sea otter and seaweed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:05.95,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.91,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:10.11,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer it spicy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:12.94,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't eat it if it's not sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:14.30,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.89,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.89,0:12:18.63,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure your portion is sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:22.17,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving special treatment to Aisaka-san again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.86,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,That will get you hated by girls, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:26.37,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,By Minori-chan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:26.80,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:29.01,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,You called for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.90,0:12:33.23,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Almost done? You're skilled, aren't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:34.94,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:36.86,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to add the roux.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.32,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you guys have to prepare for dinner—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:41.07,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, already preparing for supper?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:43.40,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Even I can help out with putting out plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:45.63,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:48.92,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.92,0:12:50.96,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Yuusaku, are you insane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:54.78,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. I heard Takasu's voice, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:56.19,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,The girls were here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:58.13,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:12:59.83,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, get yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:00.79,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:01.71,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.71,0:13:02.55,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:07.18,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,You narcissistic heaven-sent child! Give me a nude shot!{don't like child here}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.18,0:13:08.88,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it! Quit it, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:12.02,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying while looking like that, pretending to be modest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:13.56,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:18.56,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{nanka ima}Right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.76,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{kurokute}something black and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:21.92,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{wasattoshita}rather lively...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.92,0:13:23.58,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably a seaweed spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:25.62,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:26.24,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,weed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:28.04,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.23,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Yuusaku, you're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:31.16,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:33.00,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:34.12,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:38.18,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:41.51,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,There's an evil spirit lurking in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:43.74,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:45.51,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Make the curry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.61,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{uun to}{\i1}really{\i0} spicy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.51,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:53.66,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it looks so tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:55.03,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I made it with what I had available, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:58.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{kushieda no}as per Kushieda's request, I've made it as spicy as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:00.11,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.11,0:14:01.98,Default,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:05.51,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good! It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.03,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,It's weally dewishus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.40,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as spicy as I thought it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:11.32,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:13.80,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,You want to try it too, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.02,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:19.69,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:25.91,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,SPICY!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:26.82,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten spicy—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:28.93,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,—in my throat! Rather, it's hot! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.11,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:32.18,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I have received this meal with impact!{yeah this weird but she uses GATSUN (impact) + itadakimasu - since itadakimasu = receive/take food/drink - this works.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:34.79,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,There it is again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:36.21,Default-alt,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:37.19,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.25,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:41.59,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,It's super-spicy! It's super-delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:46.13,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,It does indeed have a strange quality to it that makes you keep eating it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:48.57,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... starting to feel strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:50.82,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's seconds too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.20,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:57.32,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was going to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:14:59.29,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:01.25,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna do the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.82,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, me too—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:04.46,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.69,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's because I ate spicy food.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:08.22,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I want some stomach medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:10.16,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Your stomach's hurting? But I didn't bring med—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:12.05,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka, are you feeling ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:14.02,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some stomach medicine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:16.26,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's in my room, wanna come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:18.06,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Th... That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:19.59,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.59,0:15:20.56,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Wha — eh — wai —
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:23.05,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's a chance to be alone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:24.62,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:26.00,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No! Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:27.41,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take care of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:27.99,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.74,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.01,0:15:37.83,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan's stomach hurts too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:38.68,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:39.54,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.41,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:42.83,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.90,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,You were spacing out, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:49.18,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Observing you never gets boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:50.76,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a compliment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:51.95,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You're just really complicated.{I'm getting much out of this one line because of the novels, where they elaborate on his inner thoughts of ami. I'm especially going to note this line in the notes.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.31,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:57.40,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, if you'd like, we could go to the beach toge—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:16:00.18,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takasu-kun, could you get that glass for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.73,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'll wash it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:03.27,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:06.06,Default,Ami,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.01,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Was it enough water?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:19.71,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Is it working?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:21.40,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Prob... ably...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:23.12,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:26.38,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing Aisaka in pain makes me hurt too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:29.79,Default,Yuusaku,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. If it hurts, would you like to lie down?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:37.26,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,You... have amazing cleaning techniques, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:40.29,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm doing it all the time at work, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.63,0:16:43.68,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun's curry was prepared with splendor as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:44.68,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,No. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:45.40,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:48.36,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you something great as thanks for helping out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:50.62,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it a secret from everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:57.04,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun... is the green tea flavor good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:58.94,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Oh, yeah, it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:00.55,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Not so much with the azuki one.{she means the green tea version was better than the azuki one}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.78,0:17:06.43,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,It's packed with stars here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:08.42,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:10.78,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:13.55,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what you'd call a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.05,0:17:19.31,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Ku-Kushieda, d-do you have boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:26.96,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,The seaweed spirit from earlier... you think it's still around?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:27.52,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.71,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{takasu-kun wa}Takasu-kun, have you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:31.90,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{yuurei mita koto aru?}ever seen a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:35.11,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No. I haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:38.06,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{watashi wa}I believe that ghosts exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:40.80,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{demo}But I have never seen one,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:44.19,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{mita koto ga aru-}and I don't believe the stories from people who have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:45.05,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.05,0:17:48.04,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{sore to sa-}And then, you see, I think of something else the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:53.30,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{watashi mo itsuka}I believe that one day I'll be in love, get married, and be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:57.69,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{kedo jissai}But there's nobody who has had it spelled out like that, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:03.71,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{you no naka no}I think that the existence of people in the world who are meant to love one another is a bit farfetched.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:06.74,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{datte watashi ni}I mean, I can't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:12.23,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{yappari yuurei}"There really isn't anything like ghosts, so I'll never see one in my life" — is how I have resigned myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:17.25,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{dakara shitsumon}And because of that, there is no answer to your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:19.25,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{takasu-kun wa}What about Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:21.44,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,{yuurei mieru-}Are you someone who can see ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.21,0:18:24.85,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{ore wa-}I think... I want to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.01,0:18:30.13,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{dakara shinrei spotto}Because of that, I go to places with spirits and I watch scary DVDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:32.34,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{ore, omoun dakedo sa}You see, I think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:37.30,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{reikan ga aru yatsu}people who are sensitive to spirits would be shocked the first time they saw one, wouldn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:41.72,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{mita kedo}I think there are people who have seen them, but then they tried to deny their existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:47.23,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{gyaku ni douryokushite}and on the other hand, there are those who put in an effort to finally be able to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:53.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,{dakara omae mo}Because of that, I think that you don't have to resign yourself to never seeing one in your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.14,0:18:54.93,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:56.29,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,A UFO?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:59.55,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That's a satellite.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.55,0:19:01.39,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,A satellite...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:05.69,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,What? I thought it was a UFO.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:13.94,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be great if you could see ghosts sometime, Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:14.25,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:19.18,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Because I think that there's a ghost out there that wants you to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:24.85,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why there were lots of strange things that happened today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:25.39,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:28.89,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,It's appealing to me! The seaweed spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:32.20,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:35.38,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll see them one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:36.11,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.61,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,No! Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:41.29,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:48.70,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji. I think my stomach's all better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:49.94,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:58.74,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm full! So full!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.01,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, even I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:02.76,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:04.96,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:05.94,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.91,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about {\i1}that{\i0} plan, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:11.65,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,You're not doing your part properly at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:13.29,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:16.27,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the support this time around!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:19.27,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! Am I ever tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:19.69,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:26.71,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I kept thinking about how happy I'd be after spending an entire day with Kitamura-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:29.70,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,but I was so nervous I could die an early death.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.66,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:34.70,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Though when I'm with you, I'm completely fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:36.11,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.11,0:20:36.92,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:38.43,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's so dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:41.87,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,This room is so big, yet we're sitting this close to one another...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:45.66,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the habits of being in a small apartment have stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:46.59,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:47.64,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:50.64,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:53.97,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,That dream was... rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:55.92,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:20:59.27,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:00.69,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:02.03,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:03.53,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:09.93,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did I put my bag here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:14.26,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,What is... this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.95,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,And it's somewhat slippery...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:18.46,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.85,0:21:20.40,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:24.34,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,It was in my bag... yet when I touched it earlier, it was still warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:27.16,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,as if someone had just been wearing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.33,0:21:30.12,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,My room's weird too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:32.14,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,On my pillow, there was long hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:34.76,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:36.81,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,That was prob—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:43.10,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is a dream... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.03,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.25,0:21:48.83,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,It's a continuation of that dream, living in a dog house, giving birth to dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.83,0:21:51.57,Default,Taiga,0000,0000,0000,,Then, if we close our eyes, we'll wake up sometime, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:52.99,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,We'll wake up! We'll wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:54.57,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.56,0:23:26.93,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared! I'm scared! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:29.92,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,Horror movies are scary! Ghosts are scary! Monsters are scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:30.91,Default,Ryuuji,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.91,0:23:33.44,Default,Minorin,0000,0000,0000,,But... the scariest might be UFOs...
